# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in real values.
# `.env.local` is git-ignored — never commit real keys.

# --- Booking form (Web3Forms) ---
# Create a free access key at https://web3forms.com (tied to your email).
# The form submits to Web3Forms from the browser, so this is a NEXT_PUBLIC_ var
# (visible in the page — that's expected; Web3Forms keys are public by design).
# Lock the key to your domain in the Web3Forms dashboard to prevent misuse.
# Add the same variable to your Vercel project's Environment Variables.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
